    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303530/extras/8a8dabb0d3e29ea0fa7ce2682ecc4e4e.poster.avif?t=1768910443\" width=616 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303530/extras/8a8dabb0d3e29ea0fa7ce2682ecc4e4e.webm?t=1768910443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303530/extras/8a8dabb0d3e29ea0fa7ce2682ecc4e4e.mp4?t=1768910443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一人一马走进酒馆...</strong></h2><br>通过俯视的角度讲述两个亡命之徒的故事 —— 一个过于快乐的偷盗者和一个会说话、愤世嫉 俗的马。他们抢劫银行和体验过山车般的冒险经历，在墓地召唤幽灵，同时帮助你的马朋友写 一部他正在筹划的革命性科幻小说。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303530/extras/24602a2d8405c338a1e0533bd6d0c193.poster.avif?t=1768910443\" width=616 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303530/extras/24602a2d8405c338a1e0533bd6d0c193.webm?t=1768910443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303530/extras/24602a2d8405c338a1e0533bd6d0c193.mp4?t=1768910443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>狂野和荒诞的西部世界</strong></h2><br>西部世界以外的人经常形容这里：有点狂野，满是西方的味道。到处都是牛仔、溜冰者（牛仔）、尘土飞扬的城镇和光伏发电设施。但每个人都奇怪地迷恋往痰盂里吐痰，他们最喜欢的汤 是威士忌。然而，这里也有美好的一面，比如有些人工作起来很诚实，不会给仙人掌浇太多水 ，甚至还有除了保证不饿死之外还有兴趣爱好的人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303530/extras/16826cf83f37880728859066d2e4172a.poster.avif?t=1768910443\" width=616 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303530/extras/16826cf83f37880728859066d2e4172a.webm?t=1768910443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303530/extras/16826cf83f37880728859066d2e4172a.mp4?t=1768910443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>常用的沟通工具</strong></h2><br>在一个有点狂野和有点奇怪的地方，知道如何交流是件好事。左轮手枪通常是最有说服力的论 据，尤其是在敏捷的手指和良好的弹跳物理作用的帮助下。在更复杂的讨论中，一些套索技巧 和加特林机枪将是不可替代的。同样值得记住的是，没有什么比友谊和 1000 磅重的马踢腿更 强大的了。",
